## 4. Development Patterns

### Template Structure

```
templates/
тФЬтФАтФА base/
тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА base.html     # Base template with common structure
тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА _layout.html  # Common layout elements
тФВ   тФФтФАтФА _navbar.html  # Navigation component
