```

#### Template Inheritance
```html
{# base/base.html #}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        {% block head %}{% endblock %}
    </head>
    <body>
        {% include 'base/_navbar.html' %}
        {% block content %}{% endblock %}
        {% include 'base/_alerts.html' %}
    </body>
